### Gateway health
GET http://localhost:8081/health

### Register user
POST http://localhost:8081/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nguyen Tien Dat",
  "email": "dat@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8081/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dat@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Get products
GET http://localhost:8081/products

### Add product
POST http://localhost:8081/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Adam Professional Cue",
  "brand": "Adam",
  "category": "pool cue",
  "price": 5900000,
  "description": "Gậy bida phù hợp cho người chơi bán chuyên."
}

### Get inventory
GET http://localhost:8081/inventory

### Set inventory for product 1
PATCH http://localhost:8081/inventory/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 20
}

### Create order
POST http://localhost:8081/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### Get orders
GET http://localhost:8081/orders

### Get notifications
GET http://localhost:8081/notifications
